        "synopsis": "Ko Se-Yeon (Kim Sa-Rang) is a beautiful prosecutor and she is good at her job. She gets into an accident and dies. Due to mysterious bead Abyss, Ko Se-Yeon is revived, but she now has a different appearance. Ko Se-Yeon (Park Bo-Young) now possesses a common appearance. The mysterious bead Abyss revives dead persons,  but they gain a different appearance. Their appearance depends on how good their spirit was.\n\nMeanwhile, Cha Min (An Se-Ha) is the successor of a cosmetics company. He is smart, humble and has a good heart. He is also unattractive. Cha Min gets into an accident and dies. Due to the mysterious bead Abyss, he comes back to life with a different appearance. Cha Min (Ahn Hyo-Seop) now has a handsome appearance.\n\nKo Se-Yeon begins to work as an attorney at a law firm. Cha Min begins to work for Ko Se-Yeon at the law firm.",
